div.new-reservation-log
  i.bi_doc-wboard-line
  | New reservation 
  - if activity.trackable.nil? 
    | that was removed
  - else
    | by 
    span.user-id == cell(:user, activity.owner).show_link
    - if !activity.recipient.is_owned_by?(current_restaurant)
      |  at 
      span.restaurant-id == cell(:restaurant, activity.recipient).show_link if !activity.recipient.nil?
    |  with id  
    span.reservation-id == cell(:reservation, activity.trackable).show_link
    |  created 
    span == cell(:reservation, activity.trackable).updated_timeago